### Answers

### $-2+3 = 1.$

### $5+(-3) = 5-3 = 2.$

### $-2+(-3) = -5.$

### $-2-(-3) = -2+3 = 1.$

### $3 \frac{1}{8} + \frac{3}{4} + (-2 \frac{1}{6}) = \frac{41}{24}.$

